description: I couldn't find this song on YouTube, so I decided to upload it. More information about the album: http://ubiktune.com/releases/ubi013-various-artists-wintertunes

comments.text: Such a gorgeous tune. I can imagine walking through snowdrifts in a winter forest clearing and breathing in fresh chilly. I should listen to this when winter comes (soon!). Thanks for the upload. Temp Sound Solutions is heavily underrated.
comments.author: @grogg4372
